tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE lab_test_results (
    test_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_id INT,
    test_type VARCHAR(50),
    test_result TEXT,
    test_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE blood_tests (
    test_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_id INT,
    test_type VARCHAR(50),
    test_date DATE,
    test_result TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE imaging_tests (
    test_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_id INT,
    test_type VARCHAR(50),
    test_date DATE,
    image_url VARCHAR(255)
);
